[h3 id=Aboutthegame 
	" About the game 
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Spelunker is a simple adventure game, but a difficult one. Much of the game's difficulty arises from the fact that the explorer cannot jump high or fall far, and therefore dies  
	$LF
	"extremely easily.  In  Japan,  this game's explorer is known as the most weakest hero in all action games.  Among  Internet users in Japan, the word "Spelunker" 
	$LF
	"is used to mean " too weak" or "injure oneself frequently".
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=Sumarry 
	" Sumarry
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
